@startuml
title Tutorial04 关键 Direct3D 对象关系

class ID3D11Device
class ID3D11DeviceContext
class IDXGISwapChain
class ID3D11RenderTargetView
class ID3D11VertexShader
class ID3D11PixelShader
class ID3D11InputLayout
class ID3D11Buffer {
  +VertexBuffer
  +IndexBuffer
  +ConstantBuffer
}

ID3D11Device --> IDXGISwapChain : D3D11CreateDeviceAndSwapChain()
IDXGISwapChain --> ID3D11RenderTargetView : GetBuffer(0)\nCreateRenderTargetView()
ID3D11Device --> ID3D11RenderTargetView : CreateRenderTargetView()
ID3D11Device --> ID3D11VertexShader : CreateVertexShader()
ID3D11Device --> ID3D11PixelShader : CreatePixelShader()
ID3D11Device --> ID3D11InputLayout : CreateInputLayout()
ID3D11Device --> ID3D11Buffer : CreateBuffer()

ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11RenderTargetView : OMSetRenderTargets()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11InputLayout : IASetInputLayout()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11Buffer : IASetVertexBuffers()\nIASetIndexBuffer()\nVSSetConstantBuffers()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11VertexShader : VSSetShader()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11PixelShader : PSSetShader()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> IDXGISwapChain : Present()
ID3D11DeviceContext --> ID3D11RenderTargetView : ClearRenderTargetView()

@enduml
